{"tid":138161,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[物理撚]Olber's Paradox","createTime":"2017-02-28T11:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T17:21:57.000Z","uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"873f0a8c417ef9ccca64bdc281a01da93b5b4e5e","tid":138161,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"物理廢渣求解<br />\nOlber's Paradox 有冇諗埋visible universe呢個問題<br />\n其實宇宙可以真係infinite但只係光速所限 啲光未到地球我地未睇到<br />\n即係observable universe係細過真正宇宙size<br />\n咁都仍然可以係有黑夜 但又合理地宇宙係無限<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知宇宙應該唔係無限 但個paradox是咪fail咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab276c2f4869f198682e1e5a2f8ddb2fd0a846e0","tid":138161,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"推一推 唔通連登無物理撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf0c6df45e46f63e0f8ae35a59309416794f61f","tid":138161,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩wiki完，我初頭諗點解唔會因為星既距離唔同，我地望上個天，黑色係因為d光未到<br />\n諗諗下又唔係，如果好多年前粒星都己經發光，依家我地望上去都會係見到發光，只係睇緊唔同既時間<br />\n問題就係：無限大係咪就等於有無限粒星？如果唔係，咁有d方位真係唔會望到有光，所以咪黑色<br />\n利申：phy只係讀到year1"},{"pid":"0b88687144536dafac8783b749571936193562a7","tid":138161,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"唔知呢個幫唔幫到你<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XBr4GkRnY04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXBr4GkRnY04&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Br%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ee8be9ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XBr4GkRnY04</a>"},{"pid":"2fbeafb15606a6391b7af34ebb68e877dd256a68","tid":138161,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩wiki完，我初頭諗點解唔會因為星既距離唔同，我地望上個天，黑色係因為d光未到<br />\n諗諗下又唔係，如果好多年前粒星都己經發光，依家我地望上去都會係見到發光，只係睇緊唔同既時間<br />\n問題就係：無限大係咪就等於有無限粒星？如果唔係，咁有d方位真係唔會望到有光，所以咪黑色<br />\n利申：phy只係讀到year1</blockquote><br />\n其實observable universe個範圍仲係好細<br />\n仍然可以係有星發光但仲未到地球所以黑咗㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}